16:35.208 --> 16:35.625
Because of you.

16:36.125 --> 16:36.833
Is that so?

16:37.333 --> 16:38.625
I can understand, I'm going to lose some more hair.

16:39.125 --> 16:41.291
I mean I got married thrice an not twice.

16:41.791 --> 16:44.833
And I have another daughter, which means your sister.

16:45.333 --> 16:46.958
What...three marriages?

16:47.458 --> 16:49.041
Sister. I have no sister. Get lost.

16:49.541 --> 16:51.125
Uncle!

16:51.625 --> 16:53.791
What new problem did you cook-up now?

16:54.291 --> 16:57.458
Majnu, you know that I got married twice.

16:57.958 --> 17:00.041
But actually I got married thrice.

17:00.541 --> 17:01.625
Three?

17:02.125 --> 17:03.541
Children are crying out for food..

17:04.040 --> 17:05.290
..and father's finished his 3 course-meal.

17:05.790 --> 17:07.333
And I have a daughter.

17:07.833 --> 17:09.875
Daughter?

17:10.375 --> 17:11.833
You mean another sister. - Yes

17:12.333 --> 17:14.290
People normally get sc****

17:14.790 --> 17:16.250
But in this case your own father's sc**** you.

17:16.750 --> 17:18.540
Well...there's no guarantee of this father now.

17:19.040 --> 17:20.583
My life-switch can turn-off any minute.

17:21.083 --> 17:21.833
Are you my father or a ceiling fan?

17:22.333 --> 17:22.708
On-off?

17:23.208 --> 17:23.708
What's wrong with you?

17:24.208 --> 17:27.208
My motor's damaged... Heart.

17:27.708 --> 17:30.375
Just like you got Sanjana married in a decent family..

17:30.875 --> 17:33.750
..I want you to do the same with Ranjana.

17:34.250 --> 17:35.916
That's all I do.

17:36.416 --> 17:37.625
You keep getting yourselves a new wife every time.

17:38.125 --> 17:39.708
And we find grooms for our sisters.

17:40.208 --> 17:42.000
I don't have any sister.

17:42.500 --> 17:45.791
But I have a brother.

17:46.291 --> 17:49.041
I thought he'll be overjoyed to see me.

17:49.541 --> 17:50.625
Hug me..

17:51.125 --> 17:54.166
I didn't know he'll refuse to accept me.

17:54.666 --> 17:55.750
On every 'Raksha Bandhan'..

17:56.250 --> 18:00.833
..I would see my friend's brothers and wish that I had a brother too.

18:01.333 --> 18:02.625
But when I found out that I do..

18:03.125 --> 18:05.458
..I left my exams in-between to meet him.

18:05.958 --> 18:06.791
Now I've met him.

18:07.291 --> 18:09.958
I guess I'm not destined for any brotherly love.

18:10.458 --> 18:12.291
Why not?

18:12.791 --> 18:14.000
I am there.

18:14.500 --> 18:18.458
I always wished that... I had a sister.

18:18.958 --> 18:20.750
And I've found her today.

18:21.250 --> 18:22.750
You're my sister...not his.

18:23.250 --> 18:23.791
I'll get you married.

18:24.291 --> 18:25.041
Majnu!

18:25.541 --> 18:28.291
Let it be, brother. It's not her fault.

18:28.791 --> 18:32.291
It's... - I admit it's my fault.

18:44.083 --> 18:46.208
Come.

18:46.708 --> 18:49.416
Uday, you're exactly like me.

18:49.916 --> 18:52.416
Emotional rascal.

18:52.916 --> 18:56.416
Now I can happily go on my pilgrimage.

19:05.666 --> 19:10.625
Sunder Shetty...now you can get married again.

19:11.125 --> 19:13.666
Now I can happily return India and give my exams.

19:14.166 --> 19:15.333
Your happiness is going to double-up.

19:15.833 --> 19:16.708
Soon you'll have a sister-in-law as well.

19:17.208 --> 19:18.916
