19:43.166 --> 19:44.125
What will the people of Nazabgarh say?

19:44.625 --> 19:45.666
Yes...what will they say?

19:46.166 --> 19:47.833
How can we find a decent guy so soon? - Yes.

19:48.333 --> 19:50.166
What's the hurry? Take your time.

19:50.666 --> 19:52.541
Your sister's not in a hurry nor are we.

19:53.041 --> 19:54.125
But we are.

19:54.625 --> 19:57.125
