39:43.875 --> 39:44.166
"I Love You."

39:44.666 --> 39:48.166
Wow, boss... amazing.

40:00.125 --> 40:03.625
Bhai, she's dumb.

40:11.583 --> 40:15.083
And deaf too.

40:19.500 --> 40:23.000
Damn..

40:25.875 --> 40:27.958
Bhai...she's saying "I Love You".

40:28.458 --> 40:32.291
I Love You?

40:32.791 --> 40:34.125
PVR Cinema...Sunday 12 to 3.

40:34.625 --> 40:38.250
We'll also see the film if we get the time.

40:38.750 --> 40:40.333
Bhai, she's asking for a reply.

40:40.833 --> 40:45.583
So fast. - I know.

40:46.083 --> 40:49.583
She's saying if you don't reply, she'll cut off your legs.

40:59.750 --> 41:03.250
Bhai, did you see the way you gave the flower?

41:07.208 --> 41:08.375
Who will give a flower to you?

41:08.875 --> 41:09.291
Quiet!

41:09.791 --> 41:13.291
This is for bhai... from sister-in-law.

41:40.708 --> 41:44.375
Bhai, this is a flower... not a knife.

41:44.875 --> 41:46.583
Hold it like this.

41:47.083 --> 41:50.125
Bhai, men always look for a wife that speaks less.

41:50.625 --> 41:52.458
But thankfully sister-in-law's completely mute.

41:52.958 --> 41:53.500
Yes, bhai.

41:54.000 --> 41:55.958
And there's a lot of similarity between the two of you.

41:56.458 --> 41:59.458
You never listen... and she'll never hear anyone.

41:59.958 --> 42:01.750
Right, Javed.

42:02.250 --> 42:07.750
Since bhai's fallen in love, you seem uncomfortable.

42:08.250 --> 42:09.500
Shut up.

42:10.000 --> 42:12.083
Bhai...why are you so quiet?

42:12.583 --> 42:15.375
What do I say?

42:15.875 --> 42:19.625
When she was trying to gesture her feelings..

42:20.125 --> 42:21.333
..it felt like someone was..

42:21.833 --> 42:26.041
..firing at me with a AK-47 fitted with a silencer.

42:26.541 --> 42:30.041
No sound...no bullets fired... but my heart's been shot.

43:04.500 --> 43:05.416
Boss...phone.

43:05.916 --> 43:07.083
"Majnu..."

43:07.583 --> 43:10.125
Good morning.

43:10.625 --> 43:11.333
Good morning.

43:11.833 --> 43:15.333
Good morning, how are you?

43:20.583 --> 43:22.875
Why so quiet?

43:23.375 --> 43:26.875
What are you looking at?

43:28.958 --> 43:31.041
Last night... I had an overheated discussion..

43:31.541 --> 43:33.500
..about your love with my heart.

43:34.000 --> 43:38.041
And in the morning... you two won.

43:38.541 --> 43:44.000
You're sentenced to love for life under section love.

43:44.500 --> 43:48.000
I have decided... that I will marry you.

43:48.500 --> 43:50.000
Really?

43:50.500 --> 43:51.375
Did you two hear?

43:51.875 --> 43:52.958
Yes. - I am the prince of Najabgarh now.

43:53.458 --> 43:54.333
I won! I won!

43:54.833 --> 43:57.250
Majnu's out.

43:57.750 --> 43:59.875
The real Majnu (Romeo) never got his Laila (Juliet)..

44:00.375 --> 44:01.958
..so how can this Majnu.

44:02.458 --> 44:03.250
Correct.

44:03.750 --> 44:05.125
This is going to be fun.

44:05.625 --> 44:08.291
Go and give this good news to Uday. - No!

44:08.791 --> 44:10.333
You won't do anything like that. - Why?

44:10.833 --> 44:11.333
Why?

44:11.833 --> 44:14.208
Your friend loves me a lot.

44:14.708 --> 44:17.958
What if this news shocks him to death?

44:18.458 --> 44:20.208
I know you're a very nice man.

44:20.708 --> 44:25.708
And you wouldn't want your friend, who's like a brother to you, to die.

44:26.208 --> 44:27.125
He's right.

44:27.625 --> 44:30.125
That's fine, but.. - What about our marriage?

44:30.625 --> 44:31.291
What about our marriage?

44:31.791 --> 44:33.083
Leave that to me.

44:33.583 --> 44:37.750
I know it's a bit difficult, but I'll explain him.

44:38.250 --> 44:44.416
But for my sake, you will never let him find out about our relation.

44:44.916 --> 44:46.083
You've gone crazy in love.

44:46.583 --> 44:49.500
How could you forget, that our only ancestral manor in Nazabgarh..

44:50.000 --> 44:53.000
..is on the verge of being auctioned?

44:53.500 --> 44:57.041
How will I get 20 million to save it?

44:57.541 --> 44:59.125
"Majnu..."

44:59.625 --> 45:00.333
"Laila..."

45:00.833 --> 45:01.208
Come on.

45:01.708 --> 45:02.708
Only 20 million.

45:03.208 --> 45:05.083
Tell the queen she'll get her 20 million in 30 minutes.

45:05.583 --> 45:07.875
Tell her. - Only 20 million.

45:08.375 --> 45:10.125
No need to worry.

45:10.625 --> 45:13.416
Lawyer... - Cheque book's ready.

45:13.916 --> 45:15.458
How sweet of you.

45:15.958 --> 45:17.125
You've such a big heart.

45:17.625 --> 45:20.666
I did the right thing by choosing you as my life-partner.

45:21.166 --> 45:21.958
I love you my love.

45:22.458 --> 45:23.166
I love you too, baby.

45:23.666 --> 45:29.500
I love you too.. - Boss.

45:30.000 --> 45:31.375
Why did you bring me here, Ranjana?

45:31.875 --> 45:34.291
I want to see what a big lover is he?

45:34.791 --> 45:36.666
Whether he comes here even after I warned him yesterday.

45:37.166 --> 45:39.916
"Here he comes...Ajju bhai."

45:40.416 --> 45:41.250
Ticket. - Don't want it.

45:41.750 --> 45:42.416
I am asking for your ticket.

45:42.916 --> 45:43.583
Give him the ticket.

45:44.083 --> 45:46.833
Why you..

45:47.333 --> 45:48.875
Enough...let's go.

45:49.375 --> 45:53.458
I only asked for a ticket, but you guys gave me the monthly pass instead.

45:53.958 --> 45:55.500
What? 17 guns?

45:56.000 --> 45:57.166
And adding these 3 makes it 20.

45:57.666 --> 45:58.250
But Pappu only asked for 15.

45:58.750 --> 45:59.333
Where is she?

45:59.833 --> 46:00.958
Ranjana.

46:01.458 --> 46:01.625
Look.

46:02.125 --> 46:03.375
There she is.

46:03.875 --> 46:04.541
"He'll be happy."

46:05.041 --> 46:06.541
"And listen, we'll sell these at the flea market."

46:07.041 --> 46:08.875
He's really shameless.

46:09.375 --> 46:09.541
Let him come.

46:10.041 --> 46:11.291
But don't tell Pappu. - I won't.

46:11.791 --> 46:14.583
Rascal, where are the three guns?

46:15.083 --> 46:18.583
What three guns?

46:32.166 --> 46:35.666
What is this brother?

46:49.916 --> 46:51.083
What?

46:51.583 --> 46:53.500
See

46:54.000 --> 46:58.791
Yes.. - Shut up

46:59.291 --> 47:05.250
"Baby."

47:05.750 --> 47:07.416
I'll give you any price you want.

47:07.916 --> 47:11.416
But who did you sell the gun to?

47:28.625 --> 47:30.791
Bhai, you made a mistake..

47:31.291 --> 47:32.708
..and made us pay the price.

47:33.208 --> 47:34.416
Mistake me?

47:34.916 --> 47:39.333
Bhai, she was not a school kid that you kissed her on the cheeks.

47:39.833 --> 47:42.208
You could've kissed her lips, but you kissed her cheek instead.

47:42.708 --> 47:44.250
This happened in the 70's.

47:44.750 --> 47:45.416
Shame on you.

47:45.916 --> 47:48.333
Bhai...you should've done as she did.

47:48.833 --> 47:51.000
Lip-to-lip, bhai.

47:51.500 --> 47:53.166
But you kissed her cheeks instead.

47:53.666 --> 47:55.791
Is that why she slapped me? - Yes.

47:56.291 --> 47:58.125
Sister-in-law thought you're Emraan Hashmi..

47:58.625 --> 48:01.625
..but you turned out to be Amol Palekar.

48:02.125 --> 48:04.375
What the...

48:04.875 --> 48:08.500
I made a big mistake.

48:09.000 --> 48:12.916
Why didn't you tell me earlier that he isn't the boy, It was such a big misunderstanding.

48:13.416 --> 48:15.250
I even slapped the poor guy.

48:15.750 --> 48:17.458
I wonder what he must be thinking about me.

48:17.958 --> 48:20.625
Then say sorry. - But where will I find him?

48:21.125 --> 48:24.625
No need to go anywhere, there he is.

48:33.833 --> 48:37.333
Say sorry.

48:44.083 --> 48:47.583
Liping bro, liping.

48:51.416 --> 48:54.916
That...

48:58.166 --> 49:00.958
I don't understand anything you're saying.

49:01.458 --> 49:05.791
You can talk?

49:06.291 --> 49:08.041
Of course I can. but... you can talk too?

49:08.541 --> 49:08.916
Yes.

49:09.416 --> 49:11.458
But why were you talking in gestures?

49:11.958 --> 49:15.458
Because my boys said that you're deaf and dumb.

49:22.208 --> 49:24.208
I am glad that you can talk and listen.

49:24.708 --> 49:26.791
Even I'm glad that you're not deaf or dumb.

49:27.291 --> 49:28.625
Now I can apologies.

49:29.125 --> 49:32.166
It was my mistake, why will you apologies?

49:32.666 --> 49:33.375
Your mistake?

49:33.875 --> 49:36.375
I had no idea I was supposed to kiss you on your lips.

49:36.875 --> 49:40.375
What? - Yeah!

49:58.625 --> 50:00.958
"Listen... - What?"

50:01.458 --> 50:03.416
"There's something in my heart, can I say it?"

50:03.916 --> 50:08.250
"Do you want me...to bring you the stars...like other crazy lovers?"

50:08.750 --> 50:15.916
"You can wear the bridal dress...and I'll wear a coat."

50:16.416 --> 50:18.291
"Don't delay any more."

50:18.791 --> 50:20.833
"Come be my wife."

50:21.333 --> 50:25.958
"We'll get married in Mumbai... and honeymoon in Dubai."

50:26.458 --> 50:31.000
"What's the hurry... to be your wife so soon?"

50:31.500 --> 50:36.083
"I still have to tell my brothers...about you?"

50:36.583 --> 50:41.083
"There's a feeling in my heart... and the ambiance is thrilling."

50:41.583 --> 50:46.041
"But you will have to wait... don't be a psycho."

50:46.541 --> 50:48.541
"Don't delay any more."

50:49.041 --> 50:51.000
"Come be my wife."

50:51.500 --> 50:56.291
"We'll get married in Mumbai... and honeymoon in Dubai."

50:56.791 --> 51:01.250
"What's the hurry... to be your wife so soon?"

51:01.750 --> 51:05.250
"I still have to tell my brothers...about you?"

51:22.208 --> 51:24.125
"We can be a couple..."

51:24.625 --> 51:26.708
"First you stop being a bully."

51:27.208 --> 51:29.250
"Button up your shirt completely..."

51:29.750 --> 51:31.625
"...and change your style slightly."

51:32.125 --> 51:34.291
"You're my sweetheart."

51:34.791 --> 51:36.833
"I'll do what you say."

51:37.333 --> 51:41.916
"I kissed you once... and my life changed completely."

51:42.416 --> 51:44.375
"My heart's jumping...jumping.."

51:44.875 --> 51:47.000
"How about we do lipping...lipping."

51:47.500 --> 51:54.541
"But you will have to wait...don't be a psycho."

51:55.041 --> 51:56.708
"Don't delay any more."

51:57.208 --> 51:59.291
"Come be my wife."

51:59.791 --> 52:04.250
"We'll get married in Mumbai... and honeymoon in Dubai."

52:04.750 --> 52:09.458
"What's the hurry...to be your wife so soon?"

52:09.958 --> 52:13.458
"I still have to tell my brothers...about you?"

52:45.708 --> 52:46.916
Why are you walking like this?

52:47.416 --> 52:50.958
I shutdown all my bad business' for you.

52:51.458 --> 52:51.875
I have become descent.

52:52.375 --> 52:53.750
It'll take me some time to change my style.

52:54.250 --> 52:57.000
And it will take brother lesser time to recognize you.

52:57.500 --> 52:58.416
You've changed from Ajju to Ajay..

52:58.916 --> 53:01.000
..so learn to walk and speak like a descent man.

53:01.500 --> 53:02.833
Fine...don't worry.

53:03.333 --> 53:04.333
I'll try my best.

53:04.833 --> 53:08.333
And stop using these slangs. - Okay.

53:08.833 --> 53:14.541
Please don't give brother high BP. - Okay, fine.

53:15.041 --> 53:16.833
Sir...it's still increasing, sir.

53:17.333 --> 53:19.916
Boss, you get worried over trivial reasons.

53:20.416 --> 53:22.208
It's a small thing.. - Small thing?

53:22.708 --> 53:23.666
Did your father get married three times..

53:24.166 --> 53:25.458
..and created such hassles?

53:25.958 --> 53:27.916
I've fixed Ranjana's marriage somewhere else.

53:28.416 --> 53:30.041
And now she's in love with someone else.

53:30.541 --> 53:31.500
And she's going to introduce us to him today.

53:32.000 --> 53:32.625
Is this a small thing?

53:33.125 --> 53:35.916
Boss... - Ranjana's here.

53:36.416 --> 53:37.666
Brother.

53:38.166 --> 53:39.750
What's all this? - Nothing.

53:40.250 --> 53:41.833
Just my routine checkup, everything's normal.

53:42.333 --> 53:43.125
Sit. Sit...

53:43.625 --> 53:43.833
Sit...

53:44.333 --> 53:51.875
Sir, can I sit too? - Ajay. Brother asked us both to sit.

53:52.375 --> 53:53.666
Thank you, sir.

53:54.166 --> 53:55.041
What would you like to have?

53:55.541 --> 53:57.375
Cutting..

53:57.875 --> 54:00.416
He means nothing... Nothing.

54:00.916 --> 54:01.625
I don't drink tea.

54:02.125 --> 54:07.958
Brother, I'm sure you chose a descent boy for me.

54:08.458 --> 54:11.958
But Ajay...is really nice.

54:16.916 --> 54:19.333
Brother, we really love each other.

54:19.833 --> 54:22.041
And so Ajay and I... - Marriage...

54:22.541 --> 54:23.541
You two want to get married.

54:24.041 --> 54:26.916
Are you angry? - No, no, I am not angry.

54:27.416 --> 54:29.750
It's a really small thing.

54:30.250 --> 54:32.625
If you're happy, I am happy.

54:33.125 --> 54:35.791
You're not just my responsibility, in fact you're my life.

54:36.291 --> 54:40.458
Sir...mom and dad... - All my three mothers are dead.

54:40.958 --> 54:42.416
And father will be soon.

54:42.916 --> 54:44.666
No, he meant his mom and dad.

54:45.166 --> 54:47.166
He wants to know when he can introduce them to you.

54:47.666 --> 54:49.750
Yeah...we'll meet them.

54:50.250 --> 54:52.958
Once I cancel this wedding.

54:53.458 --> 54:55.125
They are really decent people.

54:55.625 --> 54:58.375
It's really tough to explain descent people.

54:58.875 --> 55:00.041
Let me know if it gets too tough for you.

55:00.541 --> 55:01.000
Huh?

55:01.500 --> 55:04.833
He means, if it's too awkward for you..

55:05.333 --> 55:06.458
..then he'll go request them.

55:06.958 --> 55:08.000
No...it's alright.

55:08.500 --> 55:08.958
I'll handle it.

55:09.458 --> 55:09.750
Yes, sir.

55:10.250 --> 55:13.916
That's life. I'll handle it.

55:14.416 --> 55:17.666
Sir, can I say something? - Of course.

55:18.166 --> 55:20.458
You see, matches are made in heaven.

55:20.958 --> 55:23.458
And people only create problems.

55:23.958 --> 55:26.208
Like...Romeo-Juliet.

55:26.708 --> 55:28.750
Devdas-Paro. Shirin-Farhad.

55:29.250 --> 55:29.708
What?

55:30.208 --> 55:31.583
Shirin-Farhad. - Who?

55:32.083 --> 55:35.250
Shirin-Farhad? What about them?

55:35.750 --> 55:40.916
You know their love... - Knot?

55:41.416 --> 55:43.958
No...

55:44.458 --> 55:47.625
Chewing gum?

55:48.125 --> 55:49.125
Bond. - Bond.

55:49.625 --> 55:49.958
Bond!

55:50.458 --> 55:50.666
Bond! - What about it?

55:51.166 --> 55:54.125
People break that bond.

55:54.625 --> 55:57.250
But we'll get married.

55:57.750 --> 56:01.250
You're with us.

56:07.833 --> 56:09.750
Who's she in love with? - A boy...tall, handsome.

56:10.250 --> 56:12.333
Wears glasses. He seems from a descent family.

56:12.833 --> 56:13.916
Descent?

56:14.416 --> 56:17.375
We didn't exactly fix her marriage with some dacoit.

56:17.875 --> 56:18.750
How did she fall in love?

56:19.250 --> 56:20.958
Who will explain this to that old man?

56:21.458 --> 56:23.083
What old man? - That Ghunghroo...

56:23.583 --> 56:24.833
He should've been begging at our feet..

56:25.333 --> 56:27.000
..but he made him our relative instead.

56:27.500 --> 56:30.875
And now he'll make us dance to his tunes.

56:31.375 --> 56:34.375
If he finds out we've chosen someone else..

56:34.875 --> 56:36.041
..he'll curse us over and over again.

56:36.541 --> 56:37.916
We're brothers after all.

56:38.416 --> 56:38.958
We'll share it together.

56:39.458 --> 56:41.416
I'll take some... and you can take some.

56:41.916 --> 56:43.166
What about the rest?

56:43.666 --> 56:45.375
You.. - You all will take the rest.

56:45.875 --> 56:47.291
You rascals.

56:47.791 --> 56:49.666
You were all so eager in congratulating him.

56:50.166 --> 56:53.666
Now pay!

56:58.208 --> 56:59.541
You all here...so suddenly.

57:00.041 --> 57:01.083
Is everything okay?

57:01.583 --> 57:03.166
We.. - What's wrong?

57:03.666 --> 57:04.000
Come, sit.

57:04.500 --> 57:05.583
Sit.

57:06.083 --> 57:07.958
Greetings, sit.

57:08.458 --> 57:10.583
Rafiq. Get tea and snacks for the guests.

57:11.083 --> 57:12.041
Snacks?

57:12.541 --> 57:13.666
You won't get it. - What?

57:14.166 --> 57:15.000
They will cancel it.

57:15.500 --> 57:18.125
So, Uday...what is it?

57:18.625 --> 57:19.958
Shirin-Farhad.

57:20.458 --> 57:21.291
Shirin-Farhad?

57:21.791 --> 57:24.750
I mean...in love.. - I don't get it.

57:25.250 --> 57:26.916
Matches are made in heaven..

57:27.416 --> 57:28.916
This marriage isn't possible.

57:29.416 --> 57:31.375
What are you saying, Uday? - Let them say it.

57:31.875 --> 57:35.583
I was yearning to hear them say this.

57:36.083 --> 57:37.458
What are you saying?

57:37.958 --> 57:39.750
What do you mean by this marriage isn't possible? - I mean..

57:40.250 --> 57:41.916
Have you all lost your mind?

57:42.416 --> 57:45.583
I've booked everything... right from the horse to the DJ.

57:46.083 --> 57:46.541
What's more...

57:47.041 --> 57:49.791
We've even decided who's going to do the serpent dance.

57:50.291 --> 57:51.875
So now who's going to sit on the horse?

57:52.375 --> 57:53.708
Who's going to do the serpent dance?

57:54.208 --> 57:55.708
Even we fixed everything..

57:56.208 --> 57:57.125
..from our sister's Mehendi to Daler Mahendi.

57:57.625 --> 57:59.041
What? - Daler Mahendi.

57:59.541 --> 58:00.166
Daler Mahendi.

58:00.666 --> 58:02.291
But you see...she's in love with someone else.

58:02.791 --> 58:04.250
So what can I do? Please don't mind.

58:04.750 --> 58:07.958
No, no, of course not. Do you want me to distribute blankets to the poor?

58:08.458 --> 58:09.750
Why did he point towards us?

58:10.250 --> 58:11.541
He meant him.

58:12.041 --> 58:13.375
Mr. Uday Shetty. - Yes.

58:13.875 --> 58:16.000
My son agreed to marry your daughter..

58:16.500 --> 58:18.875
..without even taking a look.

58:19.375 --> 58:20.375
Without a single look. - Yes.

58:20.875 --> 58:22.666
If that decent boy finds out..

58:23.166 --> 58:26.625
..that her future wife is cozying-up with someone else..

58:27.125 --> 58:28.583
..won't that decent man be upset?

58:29.083 --> 58:31.666
It will, don't worry God's blessed me everything...

58:32.166 --> 58:33.250
Yeah right...Fame...Fortune...!

58:33.750 --> 58:36.541
Respect. - Respect? You still have respect?

58:37.041 --> 58:38.291
Yes...I still do.

58:38.791 --> 58:40.416
We'll find a girl for your son.

58:40.916 --> 58:43.916
See that. These two can't find a girl for themselves.

58:44.416 --> 58:46.000
They are roaming around like raging bulls..

58:46.500 --> 58:48.666
..and they claim they'll find a girl for my son.

58:49.166 --> 58:50.125
Right.

58:50.625 --> 58:52.291
My son would rather stay bachelor..

58:52.791 --> 58:54.916
..than marry someone from your family.

58:55.416 --> 58:57.958
And yes, if your father remarries for the fourth time..

58:58.458 --> 59:00.958
..and bring forth another sister.

59:01.458 --> 59:04.083
Then before fixing her marriage.

59:04.583 --> 59:06.416
..don't forget to ask her if she's having an affair too.

59:06.916 --> 59:07.750
Control! Control!

59:08.250 --> 59:09.083
What if she's in love?

59:09.583 --> 59:11.083
What are you saying?

59:11.583 --> 59:13.833
You shouldn't forget that they're our relatives.

59:14.333 --> 59:15.083
Relatives?

59:15.583 --> 59:18.500
They should be entombed.

59:19.000 --> 59:21.041
People swear on my decency...

59:21.541 --> 59:25.375
...but after this will I be able to face anyone.

59:25.875 --> 59:29.000
Control, Uday! Control.

59:29.500 --> 59:32.166
Boss...is your gun loaded? - Yes.

59:32.666 --> 59:37.041
Then fire... - No! It's our fault.

59:37.541 --> 59:40.041
It's not such a big mistake,

59:40.541 --> 59:42.208
He's being too smart.

59:42.708 --> 59:43.708
I'll talk to him.

59:44.208 --> 59:48.125
You? - I know how to handle people like him.

59:48.625 --> 59:50.375
Ghungroo, I was saying...

59:50.875 --> 59:53.291
Shut up crooked shoulder.

59:53.791 --> 59:56.791
Bloody rascal, scoundrel, good-for-nothing, scum.

59:57.291 --> 59:58.041
But that doesn't rhyme.

59:58.541 --> 59:59.625
Stop thinking about the rhyme.

01:00:00.125 --> 01:00:02.458
Concentrate on the cusswords.

01:00:02.958 --> 01:00:04.125
And when the brother's Majnu(Romeo)..

01:00:04.625 --> 01:00:06.500
..sister's bound to be someone's Laila(Juliet).

01:00:07.000 --> 01:00:10.291
She must be involved with someone.

01:00:10.791 --> 01:00:11.291
What are you looking at?

01:00:11.791 --> 01:00:12.333
What are you looking at?

01:00:12.833 --> 01:00:14.458
You want to hit me?

01:00:14.958 --> 01:00:16.791
Hit me. Come on...hit me.

01:00:17.291 --> 01:00:19.666
Goons...bloody goons. You will never reform.

01:00:20.166 --> 01:00:21.791
You're only wearing this garb of decency.

01:00:22.291 --> 01:00:24.208
Ghunghroo...we're embarrassed too.

01:00:24.708 --> 01:00:26.375
I don't care.

01:00:26.875 --> 01:00:30.375
Go and hide your shameless faces. - Please..

01:00:53.583 --> 01:00:57.291
Why did you come here? I told you I'll deal with them.

01:00:57.791 --> 01:00:59.916
Sir...this is my home.

01:01:00.416 --> 01:01:02.250
So Ghunghroo's a paying-guest here?

01:01:02.750 --> 01:01:03.750
Sir, he's my father.

01:01:04.250 --> 01:01:05.625
My dad.

01:01:06.125 --> 01:01:10.375
Ghunghroo...

01:01:10.875 --> 01:01:14.291
This is amazing, Ghunghroo.

01:01:14.791 --> 01:01:15.666
All this was a little hard to understand.

01:01:16.166 --> 01:01:17.375
There was a strange confusion.

01:01:17.875 --> 01:01:20.916
Actually...the boy Ranjana loves is your son.

01:01:21.416 --> 01:01:24.333
Ajay.

01:01:24.833 --> 01:01:26.416
Oh...

01:01:26.916 --> 01:01:29.541
This is truly amazing.

01:01:30.041 --> 01:01:36.166
Like I said...your sister can never choose a wrong guy.

01:01:36.666 --> 01:01:37.958
Let me introduce you.

01:01:38.458 --> 01:01:39.166
This is Majnu.

01:01:39.666 --> 01:01:43.083
My friend, business partner, brother, companion... Everything!

01:01:43.583 --> 01:01:48.541
"Majnu bhai.."

01:01:49.041 --> 01:01:49.958
Ghunghroo... - Yes.

01:01:50.458 --> 01:01:53.291
You were talking too much today. - It was nothing.

01:01:53.791 --> 01:01:56.458
Nothing. You even involved my father.

01:01:56.958 --> 01:01:58.333
I was tensed. - Tensed?

01:01:58.833 --> 01:02:02.333
Do you know what happens when the bull charges at you?

01:02:09.416 --> 01:02:11.916
This time...

01:02:12.416 --> 01:02:13.625
You can't even light a lighter.

01:02:14.125 --> 01:02:17.625
How will you fire a gun?

01:02:30.208 --> 01:02:32.791
Practice.

01:02:33.291 --> 01:02:36.791
College...knowledge.

01:02:45.958 --> 01:02:48.666
What? You don't get the boy?

01:02:49.166 --> 01:02:49.958
What are you saying?

01:02:50.458 --> 01:02:52.208
Ghunghroo's family is so decent.

01:02:52.708 --> 01:02:57.041
Even the flies in his house have hover decently.

01:02:57.541 --> 01:03:02.125
Ajay's over-smart gait.

01:03:02.625 --> 01:03:06.375
Raising his hand while meeting.

01:03:06.875 --> 01:03:10.666
Lighting a matchstick like this.

01:03:11.166 --> 01:03:13.000
Normally people from our profession do these things.

01:03:13.500 --> 01:03:17.708
Boss, these days college kids have become more stylish than us.

01:03:18.208 --> 01:03:19.416
Right. - It's become a fashion.

01:03:19.916 --> 01:03:22.416
Yes, Majnu sir. You doubt him for no reason.

01:03:22.916 --> 01:03:26.791
Exactly. Ranjana's getting engaged.

01:03:27.291 --> 01:03:29.250
Let's go, we've much to do. Come on.

01:03:29.750 --> 01:03:33.250
Let's go.

01:03:43.125 --> 01:03:45.291
Smile...this is not a funeral.

01:03:45.791 --> 01:03:47.833
It's as good as a funeral for me.

01:03:48.333 --> 01:03:49.291
After Ranjana's engagement..

01:03:49.791 --> 01:03:53.000
..both the brothers will trouble me again.

01:03:53.500 --> 01:03:55.541
There he is. - All fine?

01:03:56.041 --> 01:03:56.750
How am I looking?

01:03:57.250 --> 01:03:57.666
Very nice.

01:03:58.166 --> 01:04:01.458
Come. Let me introduce me to Ranjana's fianc.

01:04:01.958 --> 01:04:04.833
You better explain that rascal Majnu.

01:04:05.333 --> 01:04:06.625
I am explaining him. - Good

01:04:07.125 --> 01:04:09.625
Ajay!

01:04:10.125 --> 01:04:11.916
What happened? - Nothing.

01:04:12.416 --> 01:04:14.833
Ajay...Queen Padmavati.

01:04:15.333 --> 01:04:17.666
Princess of Nazabgarh...Chandni.

01:04:18.166 --> 01:04:18.875
Boss... - Huh!

01:04:19.375 --> 01:04:21.458
Sheikh sir's here. - Okay.

01:04:21.958 --> 01:04:22.083
Okay.

01:04:22.583 --> 01:04:26.083
Come on.

01:04:29.083 --> 01:04:30.958
"Hey Sheila-Munni."

01:04:31.458 --> 01:04:33.458
"Does he look like bread to you?"

01:04:33.958 --> 01:04:35.375
"Then why were you buttering him?"

01:04:35.875 --> 01:04:37.333
Hare Krishna! Hare Krishna.. - Quiet.

01:04:37.833 --> 01:04:38.666
"Quietly shell out all the money you looted.."

01:04:39.166 --> 01:04:41.250
"..under the pretext of marrying him."

01:04:41.750 --> 01:04:45.750
"When Ajju resorts to violence, he doesn't care about gender."

01:04:46.250 --> 01:04:46.666
"Right?"

01:04:47.166 --> 01:04:49.583
"Son...give us one day's time."

01:04:50.083 --> 01:04:51.541
We meet after a long time.

01:04:52.041 --> 01:04:54.791
We wouldn't have met today either, Ajju bhai.

01:04:55.291 --> 01:04:56.166
Ajay!

01:04:56.666 --> 01:04:59.833
If you tell anyone about me.. - Why would we?

01:05:00.333 --> 01:05:01.666
We don't want our secrets revealed either.

01:05:02.166 --> 01:05:05.666
Yes... - We don't.

01:05:08.625 --> 01:05:10.041
Uday sir...

01:05:10.541 --> 01:05:12.083
Shall we start with the rituals? - Of course. - Come on.

01:05:12.583 --> 01:05:16.083
Ajay, come on. - Wait a minute.

01:05:35.625 --> 01:05:37.166
Majnu, where were you?

01:05:37.666 --> 01:05:41.250
Preparing for the groom's send-off.

01:05:41.750 --> 01:05:43.875
But that only happens at the wedding.

01:05:44.375 --> 01:05:45.958
This is just the engagement. Didn't anyone tell you?

01:05:46.458 --> 01:05:48.708
We weren't told a number of things...Samadhi ji

01:05:49.208 --> 01:05:50.750
No... it's Samdhi.

01:05:51.250 --> 01:05:53.041
Slip of tongue.

01:05:53.541 --> 01:05:57.041
Because that's going to be your future.

01:05:57.541 --> 01:06:02.125
Uday...you're mistaking him for a decent boy..

01:06:02.625 --> 01:06:04.541
..but in reality he's Mumbai's biggest goon.

01:06:05.041 --> 01:06:08.541
Ajju bhai!

01:06:13.375 --> 01:06:14.666
"Majnu bhai."

01:06:15.166 --> 01:06:18.666
Kapoor!

01:06:25.958 --> 01:06:29.458
Tell us this decent rascal's history.

01:06:32.958 --> 01:06:36.208
Don't be scared, you're with Majnu now.

01:06:36.708 --> 01:06:37.916
This is Ajju bhai.

01:06:38.416 --> 01:06:40.250
Mumbai Police's biggest headache.

01:06:40.750 --> 01:06:42.625
Riots...vandalism...

01:06:43.125 --> 01:06:46.625
Ransom, Extortion, money-laundering, Illegal-possession

01:07:05.416 --> 01:07:06.583
Did you hear?

01:07:07.083 --> 01:07:10.583
And most importantly... he isn't even his son.

01:07:19.000 --> 01:07:22.291
You said even the flies at Ghunghroo's home are decent.

01:07:22.791 --> 01:07:26.458
Now do you see what kind of family... and insects they really are?

01:07:26.958 --> 01:07:28.833
Majnu, please listen to me..

01:07:29.333 --> 01:07:31.000
The Lord's blessed us with two ears and one mouth.

01:07:31.500 --> 01:07:33.041
So talk less and hear more.

01:07:33.541 --> 01:07:37.333
Majnu...please talk to me. - Shut up.

01:07:37.833 --> 01:07:41.333
Not a word more, or I will kill you.

01:07:45.833 --> 01:07:46.916
What did you say?

01:07:47.416 --> 01:07:47.708
What?

01:07:48.208 --> 01:07:50.083
Forget the rhyme, concentrate on the cusswords.

01:07:50.583 --> 01:07:52.208
You made me concentrate on the cusswords..

01:07:52.708 --> 01:07:55.916
..and failed to concentrate on your son.

01:07:56.416 --> 01:08:00.250
You want to let our innocent sister marry this goon.

01:08:00.750 --> 01:08:04.000
You want to ruin her life and our respect.

01:08:04.500 --> 01:08:06.250
Boss, is your gun loaded.

01:08:06.750 --> 01:08:09.458
There's a huge crowd gathered here, what can I do?

01:08:09.958 --> 01:08:10.833
Don't do anything.

01:08:11.333 --> 01:08:11.583
Control.

01:08:12.083 --> 01:08:13.708
He's completely changed now, he's become descent.

01:08:14.208 --> 01:08:17.832
We couldn't reform yet, you think he can.

01:08:18.332 --> 01:08:22.041
Control. Majnu...control.

01:08:22.541 --> 01:08:24.457
We're Uday-Majnu.

01:08:24.957 --> 01:08:26.207
Uday-Majnu.

01:08:26.707 --> 01:08:29.207
We've done everything that's evil.

01:08:29.707 --> 01:08:31.332
And you want to outsmart us.

01:08:31.832 --> 01:08:34.416
He's humiliating them, that's okay..

01:08:34.916 --> 01:08:36.666
..but why is he humiliating us as well?

01:08:37.166 --> 01:08:38.416
Listen to.. - Get lost.

01:08:38.916 --> 01:08:39.666
Listen to me... - Get out.

01:08:40.166 --> 01:08:40.791
Listen to me.. - Get lost...

01:08:41.291 --> 01:08:43.166
Listen to...

01:08:43.666 --> 01:08:45.332
Hey!

01:08:45.832 --> 01:08:49.332
He's my father!

01:08:51.041 --> 01:08:54.082
And I am yours.

01:08:54.582 --> 01:08:57.375
If you touch him again, I'll break your arm later..

01:08:57.875 --> 01:09:00.125
..and rip it off first.

01:09:00.625 --> 01:09:04.125
Bloody...street thug, don't forget..

01:09:04.625 --> 01:09:05.875
..we just recently turned decent.

01:09:06.375 --> 01:09:08.957
But before this I was a goon too. - You were...

01:09:09.457 --> 01:09:10.832
But I still am one.

01:09:11.332 --> 01:09:15.957
And this bloody fool...couldn't describe what a big goon I really am.

01:09:16.457 --> 01:09:18.500
Go to Mumbai and ask anyone.

01:09:19.000 --> 01:09:22.707
I've more cases than the number of local trains.

01:09:23.207 --> 01:09:24.500
And tell me one thing..

01:09:25.000 --> 01:09:27.832
His mobile...my sim.

01:09:28.332 --> 01:09:31.707
Who are you to give a miss call?

01:09:32.207 --> 01:09:36.666
His sister...my love... who are you to interfere?

01:09:37.166 --> 01:09:39.125
I am her brother as well.

01:09:39.625 --> 01:09:40.207
Majnu.

01:09:40.707 --> 01:09:43.500
All these bloody Majnu's get stoned in the end.

01:09:44.000 --> 01:09:45.082
You can't find a Juliet for yourself..

01:09:45.582 --> 01:09:49.500
..and now you want to interfere with the one I am getting.

01:09:50.000 --> 01:09:53.082
Till today... I got everything I wanted.

01:09:53.582 --> 01:09:56.666
And now your sister dwells in my heart.

01:09:57.166 --> 01:09:58.541
Whether we get engaged or not..

01:09:59.041 --> 01:10:02.208
..but she will get married, with only me.

01:10:02.708 --> 01:10:06.125
End of story!

01:10:06.625 --> 01:10:08.291
What are you all waiting for?

01:10:08.791 --> 01:10:12.291
Throw this rascal out.

01:10:56.583 --> 01:10:58.291
I told you not to turn decent.

01:10:58.791 --> 01:11:02.291
Now you'll have to pay.

01:11:32.166 --> 01:11:35.666
I know 2006 ways to break 206 bones.

01:12:02.666 --> 01:12:08.250
Whether you're a blood-brother or distant.

01:12:08.750 --> 01:12:12.250
I'll rip anyone apart that tries to interfere with my love.

01:12:19.333 --> 01:12:22.833
You made pigeons sit on decent people, didn't you?

01:12:30.458 --> 01:12:32.416
But I am not that decent.

01:12:32.916 --> 01:12:34.125
"Ajju bhai."

01:12:34.625 --> 01:12:36.500
Those who mess with me...

01:12:37.000 --> 01:12:37.916
...I rip him apart.

01:12:38.416 --> 01:12:40.666
"Ajju bhai."

01:12:41.166 --> 01:12:45.583
You can't imagine what will be sitting on your heads?

01:12:46.083 --> 01:12:47.041
What?

01:12:47.541 --> 01:12:51.041
What?

01:13:27.208 --> 01:13:29.333
Look, crow.

01:13:29.833 --> 01:13:33.333
Crow...Crowww...

01:13:47.791 --> 01:13:51.291
Control

01:13:54.625 --> 01:13:58.125
Control Uday.

01:14:31.083 --> 01:14:34.583
Control.

01:14:36.708 --> 01:14:38.416
Control

01:14:38.916 --> 01:14:41.791
Majnu...now Uday isn't confused anymore.

01:14:42.291 --> 01:14:43.625
You were absolutely right.

01:14:44.125 --> 01:14:45.791
Decency is like a bubble.

01:14:46.291 --> 01:14:48.916
It has no value. It's worth nothing.

01:14:49.416 --> 01:14:50.125
What's wrong, boss?

01:14:50.625 --> 01:14:52.458
I got excited after a long time..

01:14:52.958 --> 01:14:54.333
..so I got a catch in my body.

01:14:54.833 --> 01:14:56.958
There are only two things this world values.

01:14:57.458 --> 01:15:02.083
Property...and rascals!

01:15:02.583 --> 01:15:05.541
I thought I'll make do with words, not bullets..

01:15:06.041 --> 01:15:09.000
..and buried my guns, but it's time to get them out now.

01:15:09.500 --> 01:15:11.916
I knew we'll need them.

01:15:12.416 --> 01:15:14.708
Hey...did you get the weapons?

01:15:15.208 --> 01:15:16.791
I found the bullets, but still looking for the guns.

01:15:17.291 --> 01:15:18.791
Hurry up...hurry up.

01:15:19.291 --> 01:15:22.666
That bloody novice made crows sit on us.

01:15:23.166 --> 01:15:27.375
Now we'll make those crows sit at his oblation.

01:15:27.875 --> 01:15:28.625
We'll give him salvation.

01:15:29.125 --> 01:15:29.916
That's more like it.

01:15:30.416 --> 01:15:32.583
Hey...did you find the guns? - Yes, I did.

01:15:33.083 --> 01:15:34.458
I even found some missiles, should I take them along too.

01:15:34.958 --> 01:15:36.458
Why don't you take the tank along too?

01:15:36.958 --> 01:15:40.375
We're going to kill Ajju, not attack Israel.

01:15:40.875 --> 01:15:42.208
He even took my favorite goggle.

01:15:42.708 --> 01:15:45.083
Uday...Majnu.

01:15:45.583 --> 01:15:47.250
You two didn't tell me..

01:15:47.750 --> 01:15:49.083
..that you're related to Ajju bhai.

01:15:49.583 --> 01:15:53.208
How can Badshah Khan take money from Ajju's brothers-in-law.

01:15:53.708 --> 01:15:55.208
Hey fatso...

01:15:55.708 --> 01:15:58.375
We've no relation with Ajju anymore.

01:15:58.875 --> 01:15:59.916
We've broken all ties.

01:16:00.416 --> 01:16:03.291
What? You broke it off, not him.

01:16:03.791 --> 01:16:04.958
This is all good if he breaks it.

01:16:05.458 --> 01:16:07.458
And he only breaks bones.

01:16:07.958 --> 01:16:10.000
Whether it's the Ace of spades... and Ajju's punch..

01:16:10.500 --> 01:16:12.500
..both mean game over.

01:16:13.000 --> 01:16:14.625
Don't lock horns with him.

01:16:15.125 --> 01:16:17.750
Go fall at his feet and apologies.

01:16:18.250 --> 01:16:20.250
And you do remember where the feet are, don't you? It's this.

01:16:20.750 --> 01:16:23.083
And don't let go until he doesn't forgive you.

01:16:23.583 --> 01:16:25.541
Uday...Uday...Uday... you're the sensible one.

01:16:26.041 --> 01:16:26.541
You've got brains.

01:16:27.041 --> 01:16:29.041
You know, if he doesn't forgive you..

01:16:29.541 --> 01:16:35.083
..he'll rip Uday and Shetty apart.

01:16:35.583 --> 01:16:38.000
Where's everyone?

01:16:38.500 --> 01:16:42.000
Right behind you!

01:16:49.791 --> 01:16:51.041
Stop these fools.

01:16:51.541 --> 01:16:54.375
If they die, we won't get any more credit.

01:16:54.875 --> 01:16:57.125
Stupid fools want to wage a war at the age of dying their hair. Rascals...

01:16:57.625 --> 01:16:58.375
Come, dear.

01:16:58.875 --> 01:17:00.541
You called them, didn't you?

01:17:01.041 --> 01:17:02.083
Where are you two going to die?

01:17:02.583 --> 01:17:05.708
See...they've already made up their mind.. - That we'll die.

01:17:06.208 --> 01:17:07.875
Yes. If Ajju hits you, you two will be dead.

01:17:08.375 --> 01:17:09.583
And if you two kill Ajju..

01:17:10.083 --> 01:17:13.666
..you'll either be sentenced to death or imprisoned for life.

01:17:14.166 --> 01:17:18.625
At this age, life imprisonment is as good as death sentence.

01:17:19.125 --> 01:17:19.958
Did you two ever think..

01:17:20.458 --> 01:17:22.458
..what will happen to me after you're dead?

01:17:22.958 --> 01:17:24.166
What's wrong with you two?

01:17:24.666 --> 01:17:26.041
You're so decent and sensible..

01:17:26.541 --> 01:17:28.208
..and want to fight that petty goon Ajju.

01:17:28.708 --> 01:17:30.875
When a decent man's honor is at stake..

01:17:31.375 --> 01:17:33.375
..then he's the biggest goon of all.

01:17:33.875 --> 01:17:35.166
I told you to get the car.

01:17:35.666 --> 01:17:37.208
I will slap you.. - Go get it.

01:17:37.708 --> 01:17:39.958
Stop these fools, mom.

01:17:40.458 --> 01:17:43.791
Fine, go on. My daughter will face her fate.

01:17:44.291 --> 01:17:45.583
But did you ever think..

01:17:46.083 --> 01:17:48.541
..what will happen to your sister after you two?

01:17:49.041 --> 01:17:52.375
Uday, God has blessed you with everything.

01:17:52.875 --> 01:17:55.625
But what does your sister have...except for you?

01:17:56.125 --> 01:18:00.208
Use your brains instead of using your hands and legs.

01:18:00.708 --> 01:18:03.583
And strike at Ajju's heart.

01:18:04.083 --> 01:18:07.583
When you can kill him with sugar, why give him poison?

01:18:13.166 --> 01:18:15.250
They fixed your marriage with someone else!

01:18:15.750 --> 01:18:16.333
I will kill those two.

01:18:16.833 --> 01:18:17.541
End of problems. - Ajju..

01:18:18.041 --> 01:18:19.125
Fine. Kill them.

01:18:19.625 --> 01:18:21.750
So that there's no difference between you and them.

01:18:22.250 --> 01:18:24.291
So will you marry the guy they chose for you?

01:18:24.791 --> 01:18:28.916
I would prefer to die first. - Dear!

01:18:29.416 --> 01:18:31.750
I think there's only one option left.

01:18:32.250 --> 01:18:33.208
You two should elope and get married.

01:18:33.708 --> 01:18:38.375
No, uncle. I cannot humiliate my brothers.

01:18:38.875 --> 01:18:42.125
I will get married only with their consent.

01:18:42.625 --> 01:18:44.208
Look, dear. They would prefer to die..

01:18:44.708 --> 01:18:47.416
..rather than giving their consent willingly.

01:18:47.916 --> 01:18:49.125
Don't worry.

01:18:49.625 --> 01:18:52.041
You will either marry me or no one.

01:18:52.541 --> 01:18:53.125
How?

01:18:53.625 --> 01:18:55.875
