01:19:23.666 --> 01:19:25.375
But after hearing about Wanted..

01:19:25.875 --> 01:19:29.041
..I feel like someone shoved an electric pole down my...

01:19:29.541 --> 01:19:33.625
You don't know Wanted bhai!

01:19:34.125 --> 01:19:37.625
Wanted bhai!

01:19:44.416 --> 01:19:47.458
"Wanted bhai!"

01:19:47.958 --> 01:19:51.458
"Wanted bhai!"

01:20:14.416 --> 01:20:17.500
"Welcome... - Wanted bhai!"

01:20:18.000 --> 01:20:19.083
"Wanted bhai!"

01:20:19.583 --> 01:20:20.916
Welcome...Welcome...

01:20:21.416 --> 01:20:23.500
Uday-Majnu.

01:20:24.000 --> 01:20:26.333
How did you know it's us?

01:20:26.833 --> 01:20:27.875
This is my island, not America..

01:20:28.375 --> 01:20:35.416
..where anyone can come in without permission.

01:20:35.916 --> 01:20:37.041
And secondly..

01:20:37.541 --> 01:20:46.166
You two still use that cheap perfume that's available at the flea market.

01:20:46.666 --> 01:20:50.166
Yes...

01:20:53.666 --> 01:20:58.583
