01:21:55.375 --> 01:21:55.750
Leave me.

01:21:56.250 --> 01:21:59.750
What did this boy do now? - Let go.

01:22:03.541 --> 01:22:04.833
Honey.

01:22:05.333 --> 01:22:05.875
No...no...

01:22:06.375 --> 01:22:07.291
Honey.

01:22:07.791 --> 01:22:10.625
Son...not again...

01:22:11.125 --> 01:22:13.666
Bloody fools...I told you to keep him away from drugs.

01:22:14.166 --> 01:22:16.416
You useless bloody..

01:22:16.916 --> 01:22:17.833
Honey...son.

01:22:18.333 --> 01:22:20.416
What else can I do?

01:22:20.916 --> 01:22:22.916
