01:22:23.416 --> 01:22:24.125
I.. - I hate you!

01:22:24.625 --> 01:22:26.791
I hate you!

01:22:27.291 --> 01:22:30.583
Honey.. - I hate you!

01:22:31.083 --> 01:22:34.416
Why is Honey so angry with you?

01:22:34.916 --> 01:22:37.541
What wish didn't you fulfill?

01:22:38.041 --> 01:22:42.666
I'm prepared to give my life for his every desire.

01:22:43.166 --> 01:22:46.416
But this time I looked everywhere to fulfill his wish..

01:22:46.916 --> 01:22:50.541
