01:23:26.458 --> 01:23:27.208
Honey.

01:23:27.708 --> 01:23:29.208
Honey, my son.

01:23:29.708 --> 01:23:30.791
What have you done?

01:23:31.291 --> 01:23:33.458
You're my world, son, I won't let anything happen to you.

01:23:33.958 --> 01:23:36.666
She's my world, dad.

01:23:37.166 --> 01:23:40.666
She's my world.

01:23:43.875 --> 01:23:47.625
This girl that's in your paintings..

01:23:48.125 --> 01:23:53.458
..I will soon make her your reality, son.

01:23:53.958 --> 01:24:00.916
Not just her, I'll abduct her entire family, in fact the entire city.

01:24:01.416 --> 01:24:02.958
She will marry only you, son.

01:24:03.458 --> 01:24:06.958
Every drop of your blood will become the vermillion on her forehead.

01:24:15.833 --> 01:24:16.708
We came here to hit the final nail..

01:24:17.208 --> 01:24:18.166
..but the hammer fell on our head instead.

01:24:18.666 --> 01:24:19.958
On one side is that goon Ajju..

01:24:20.458 --> 01:24:22.791
