01:24:40.625 --> 01:24:41.250
And listen up.

01:24:41.750 --> 01:24:43.291
No one should know about this.

01:24:43.791 --> 01:24:46.583
We swear we won't tell anyone. - Let's go. Come on.

01:24:47.083 --> 01:24:49.041
"Welcome."

01:24:49.541 --> 01:24:51.791
"Welcome."

01:24:52.291 --> 01:24:55.791
"Welcome. Welcome. Welcome."

01:25:06.500 --> 01:25:10.458
Thank you...thank you.

01:25:10.958 --> 01:25:12.083
Majnu, God's blessed me with everything

01:25:12.583 --> 01:25:13.791
Fame, fortune, honor...

01:25:14.291 --> 01:25:15.208
And the groom's decent too.

01:25:15.708 --> 01:25:16.833
Once my sister gets married without any problems..

01:25:17.333 --> 01:25:17.958
..I will take a skinny dip.

01:25:18.458 --> 01:25:19.166
You mean take a dip in Ganga.

01:25:19.666 --> 01:25:21.375
We both will take a dip and drown those two.

01:25:21.875 --> 01:25:22.458
Yes.

01:25:22.958 --> 01:25:25.541
Who? - That bull and the blind.

01:25:26.041 --> 01:25:27.083
Wanted and Ajju.

01:25:27.583 --> 01:25:29.333
Don't mention those two rascals.

01:25:29.833 --> 01:25:32.916
Forget them.

01:25:33.416 --> 01:25:36.458
"Wanted bhai."

01:25:36.958 --> 01:25:37.833
"Wanted bhai."

01:25:38.333 --> 01:25:41.833
Wanted.

01:25:45.875 --> 01:25:47.875
"Welcome.. - Wanted bhai."

01:25:48.375 --> 01:25:49.125
Wanted sir.

01:25:49.625 --> 01:25:50.333
Welcome. - Welcome.

01:25:50.833 --> 01:25:52.291
Your sister's getting married..

01:25:52.791 --> 01:25:56.291
..and you forgot to invite the groom.

01:26:00.250 --> 01:26:02.041
It was a joke. Joke.

01:26:02.541 --> 01:26:03.208
Joke.

01:26:03.708 --> 01:26:07.500
But the truth is Honey will soon get married too.

01:26:08.000 --> 01:26:08.125
I see.

01:26:08.625 --> 01:26:09.208
We were informed that..

01:26:09.708 --> 01:26:16.500
..he's going to find the love of his life in this wedding.

01:26:17.000 --> 01:26:17.833
Find the girl?

01:26:18.333 --> 01:26:21.833
Who told you? - My new friend did.

01:26:33.750 --> 01:26:37.250
No, boss.

01:26:46.208 --> 01:26:51.375
Madam, I.. - You told Ajju that Wanted's son loves Ranjana as well.

01:26:51.875 --> 01:26:54.000
No. - Shut up.

01:26:54.500 --> 01:26:56.375
What a way to stop the marriage.

01:26:56.875 --> 01:27:03.166
Your moves are better than those on the chessboard.

01:27:03.666 --> 01:27:05.166
Why did you decorate the place?

01:27:05.666 --> 01:27:06.791
Is someone getting married?

01:27:07.291 --> 01:27:09.375
We didn't decorate this place for dancing.

01:27:09.875 --> 01:27:11.208
I asked because I don't see the bride and groom anywhere.

01:27:11.708 --> 01:27:12.333
You will...you will.

01:27:12.833 --> 01:27:14.958
The wedding procession will arrive soon.

01:27:15.458 --> 01:27:17.166
Will the bride arrive with the guests?

01:27:17.666 --> 01:27:19.458
She must be right here, isn't it?

01:27:19.958 --> 01:27:21.083
So not get her blessed by this fuse bulb..

01:27:21.583 --> 01:27:23.041
I mean Wanted Bhai.

01:27:23.541 --> 01:27:26.250
Where is the girl? - There she is.

01:27:26.750 --> 01:27:28.375
Majnu.

01:27:28.875 --> 01:27:29.250
Come.

01:27:29.750 --> 01:27:31.375
Let me introduce you to the guests.

01:27:32.208 --> 01:27:33.958
Ranjana, that Ajju. - I know..

01:27:34.458 --> 01:27:35.458
Ajju is such a rascal.

01:27:35.958 --> 01:27:38.083
He brought Wanted and Honey here to spoil the wedding.

01:27:38.583 --> 01:27:39.875
I should cover my face, right? - Yes.

01:27:40.375 --> 01:27:43.333
You do that.

01:27:43.833 --> 01:27:46.083
Now watch the fun.

01:27:46.583 --> 01:27:48.000
What's wrong, sir?

01:27:48.500 --> 01:27:51.250
We're heading in the wrong direction.

01:27:51.750 --> 01:27:56.291
The fragrance is coming from this side.

01:27:56.791 --> 01:27:58.875
Come. - The blind guy's coming here.

01:27:59.375 --> 01:28:01.375
This is the queen of...Nazabgarh.

01:28:01.875 --> 01:28:02.625
How do you do?

01:28:03.125 --> 01:28:05.250
And he is.. - Everyone knows him.

01:28:05.750 --> 01:28:07.458
Wanted sir, this is Chandni. - Hello.

01:28:07.958 --> 01:28:08.333
My daughter.

01:28:08.833 --> 01:28:12.208
My... - I mean mine.

01:28:12.708 --> 01:28:15.625
I was wondering, I haven't gone hunting for a long time..

01:28:16.125 --> 01:28:19.125
..so who fired the gun.

01:28:19.625 --> 01:28:22.625
It was a joke. Joke.

01:28:23.125 --> 01:28:24.000
There's still time.

01:28:24.500 --> 01:28:26.250
The decoration's the same, so are the guests.

01:28:26.750 --> 01:28:28.125
Just change the groom, what say?

01:28:28.625 --> 01:28:32.125
B****

01:28:33.333 --> 01:28:34.833
Here comes Ranjana.

01:28:35.333 --> 01:28:38.166
Judging by her long veil..

01:28:38.666 --> 01:28:41.041
..it's even longer than the curtains on our windows.

01:28:41.541 --> 01:28:42.250
No, it's our tradition.

01:28:42.750 --> 01:28:43.541
And we've another tradition.

01:28:44.041 --> 01:28:46.375
Only the groom gets to take the veil of after the wedding.

01:28:46.875 --> 01:28:48.416
Ohh...

01:28:48.916 --> 01:28:52.416
Then I'll have to do something about this tradition.

