01:29:10.791 --> 01:29:13.708
"The damsel's hiding behind the veil."

01:29:14.208 --> 01:29:16.625
"And she's stolen my heart."

01:29:17.125 --> 01:29:23.708
"The sweet sound of your bracelets."

01:29:24.208 --> 01:29:27.125
"The sweet sound of your bracelets."

01:29:27.625 --> 01:29:30.875
"Makes me hover around you, sweetheart."

01:29:31.375 --> 01:29:35.500
"The wedding drums are resonating.."

01:29:36.000 --> 01:29:37.708
"..all around, sweetheart."

01:29:38.208 --> 01:29:41.000
"My eyes have locked with yours."

01:29:41.500 --> 01:29:45.000
"Everyone says this couple's perfect."

01:29:50.875 --> 01:29:54.375
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:29:57.875 --> 01:30:01.375
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:30:14.333 --> 01:30:19.958
"My earrings...tinkle only for you."

01:30:20.458 --> 01:30:27.708
"My heart's grown sentimental...only for you."

01:30:28.208 --> 01:30:33.750
"Since we met...everyone else was jealous."

01:30:34.250 --> 01:30:42.083
"Since we got together... everyone was against me."

01:30:42.583 --> 01:30:43.916
"Stop flirting with the girl."

01:30:44.416 --> 01:30:45.666
"Put a full stop on your love."

01:30:46.166 --> 01:30:48.958
"Romance has ruined many lives."

01:30:49.458 --> 01:30:51.125
"We're drunk to the core."

01:30:51.625 --> 01:30:52.708
"If you take this any further."

01:30:53.208 --> 01:30:55.250
"We'll teach you a lesson."

01:30:55.750 --> 01:30:59.250
"And you'll enjoy it."

01:31:02.208 --> 01:31:05.708
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:31:09.250 --> 01:31:12.750
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:31:25.958 --> 01:31:28.000
It was a joke.

01:31:28.500 --> 01:31:32.000
Just a joke.

01:31:33.125 --> 01:31:36.250
"There's a uproar all around."

01:31:36.750 --> 01:31:38.500
"You make me complete."

01:31:39.000 --> 01:31:43.041
"You're the one for me."

01:31:43.541 --> 01:31:46.458
"You announced to the world."

01:31:46.958 --> 01:31:52.958
"My first romantic flick...is a hit."

01:31:53.458 --> 01:31:54.916
"Your love is filmy."

01:31:55.416 --> 01:31:56.666
"Don't take such risks."

01:31:57.166 --> 01:32:00.000
"You don't know what your climax is."

01:32:00.500 --> 01:32:01.916
"Stop blowing the trumpet."

01:32:02.416 --> 01:32:03.625
"We will never give you green signal."

01:32:04.125 --> 01:32:06.125
"Park your car on the side."

01:32:06.625 --> 01:32:10.125
"Move aside."

01:32:13.250 --> 01:32:16.750
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:32:20.166 --> 01:32:23.666
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:32:27.125 --> 01:32:28.791
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:32:29.291 --> 01:32:31.333
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:32:31.833 --> 01:32:34.583
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:32:35.083 --> 01:32:38.583
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:12.666 --> 01:33:13.958
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

