"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:15.916 --> 01:33:17.083
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:17.583 --> 01:33:18.625
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:19.125 --> 01:33:20.291
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:20.791 --> 01:33:22.000
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:22.500 --> 01:33:23.458
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:23.958 --> 01:33:27.666
"The wedding trumpets are blaring."

01:33:28.166 --> 01:33:31.666
Take everyone to our island.

01:34:11.833 --> 01:34:12.958
Honey, my son.

01:34:13.458 --> 01:34:15.458
Your birthday's on the 13th.

01:34:15.958 --> 01:34:17.083
And I've decided that..

01:34:17.583 --> 01:34:20.000
..you and Ranjana will get engaged on the same day.

01:34:20.500 --> 01:34:24.333
Dad. You are the greatest dad.

01:34:24.833 --> 01:34:26.958
Thank you so much, dad. I love you.

01:34:27.458 --> 01:34:31.583
This engagement isn't possible!

01:34:32.083 --> 01:34:33.333
What did you say?

01:34:33.833 --> 01:34:35.791
I didn't hear you clearly.

01:34:36.291 --> 01:34:37.875
Brother said this engagement isn't possible.

01:34:38.375 --> 01:34:44.083
Majnu...Uday, this isn't your engagement.

01:34:44.583 --> 01:34:46.458
This is my son's engagement.

01:34:46.958 --> 01:34:48.666
This engagement isn't possible because he's your son.

01:34:49.166 --> 01:34:49.291
Uday!

01:34:49.791 --> 01:34:53.291
They'll directly get married.

01:34:55.958 --> 01:34:58.875
Your son loves our sister.

01:34:59.375 --> 01:35:01.416
It's not right to make lovers suffer for so long.

01:35:01.916 --> 01:35:03.166
You made me really happy, Uday.

01:35:03.666 --> 01:35:05.583
For a second I thought you're against dad's decision.

01:35:06.083 --> 01:35:11.833
Yes...I was already seeing a lot of dead bodies before the engagement.

01:35:12.333 --> 01:35:15.791
Joke...it was a joke.

01:35:16.291 --> 01:35:17.916
Uday.

01:35:18.416 --> 01:35:21.916
Congratulation Uday

01:35:34.583 --> 01:35:36.208
What did you do, Uday?

01:35:36.708 --> 01:35:37.791
You've lost your mind.

01:35:38.291 --> 01:35:40.875
Yes, I wanted to teach that Ajju a lesson.

01:35:41.375 --> 01:35:43.416
It's your ego... your obstinacy.

01:35:43.916 --> 01:35:46.458
You're ruining Ranjana's life. - Yes, it is my obstinacy.

01:35:46.958 --> 01:35:48.625
He'll be ruined along with Ranjana.

01:35:49.125 --> 01:35:51.166
You've gone crazy, have you lost your mind.

01:35:51.666 --> 01:35:52.083
Shut up!

01:35:52.583 --> 01:35:54.541
Ranjana is my sister.

01:35:55.041 --> 01:35:56.333
I can take any decision I want.

01:35:56.833 --> 01:35:58.666
Who are you to interfere?

01:35:59.166 --> 01:36:02.916
Who am I? Ranjana's my sister too.

01:36:03.416 --> 01:36:08.833
Don't forget, Majnu can give up his life for the right cause..

01:36:09.333 --> 01:36:11.708
