01:36:12.208 --> 01:36:13.333
You will kill me.

01:36:13.833 --> 01:36:14.708
Me?

01:36:15.208 --> 01:36:17.291
Kill me!

01:36:17.791 --> 01:36:18.750
Kill me!

01:36:19.250 --> 01:36:21.375
Everything is fair in love and war.

01:36:21.875 --> 01:36:24.791
It's his love... and I'm going to wage a war.

01:36:25.291 --> 01:36:27.958
Even if I've to squander everything I have..

01:36:28.458 --> 01:36:30.000
..I won't lose to that Ajju.

01:36:30.500 --> 01:36:34.000
I would rather break, but not bow..

01:36:47.708 --> 01:36:48.083
Where's my phone?

01:36:48.583 --> 01:36:51.000
My phone. - Here..

01:36:51.500 --> 01:36:55.000
Sir. What happened?

01:36:57.833 --> 01:37:00.333
Why are you crying? Get the car! Get the car!

01:37:00.833 --> 01:37:05.375
No point, boss... Uday sir..

01:37:05.875 --> 01:37:07.208
What did you say?

01:37:07.708 --> 01:37:09.708
I'll rip you apart and bury you alive.

01:37:10.208 --> 01:37:12.583
Uday is going to be fine.

01:37:13.083 --> 01:37:13.916
Uday..

01:37:14.416 --> 01:37:15.125
Talk to me.

01:37:15.625 --> 01:37:18.583
I raised my voice... hit me.

01:37:19.083 --> 01:37:20.041
Rip me apart.

01:37:20.541 --> 01:37:21.208
But please get up.

01:37:21.708 --> 01:37:23.083
Get up, Uday. Get up.

01:37:23.583 --> 01:37:28.458
Boss, God's will.. - What God?

01:37:28.958 --> 01:37:32.583
Just because You're God doesn't mean You can do anything..

01:37:33.083 --> 01:37:34.375
..and I'll do nothing.

01:37:34.875 --> 01:37:37.666
I will set the world on fire.

01:37:38.166 --> 01:37:41.291
Burn it down to ashes!

01:37:41.791 --> 01:37:45.166
Uday...get up.

01:37:45.666 --> 01:37:48.416
I've no one in this world except for you.

01:37:48.916 --> 01:37:54.583
Don't leave your Majnu alone.

01:37:55.083 --> 01:37:58.666
